description: This Java class 'ResultService' provides business logic for managing and exposing result data in a backend application, including listing results, downloading artifacts, and converting model entities to response DTOs.

classes.name: ResultService
classes.description: A service class for managing fine-tuning results, providing methods to list results, download result artifacts, and save results.

methods.name: list
methods.description: Retrieves all results and maps them to ResultResponse DTOs.

methods.name: downloadArtifact
methods.description: Fetches a result by ID and loads its artifact as a downloadable resource.

methods.name: save
methods.description: Persists a FinetuneResult entity to the repository.

methods.name: toResponse
methods.description: Converts a FinetuneResult entity to a ResultResponse DTO.
